-- KB Home Reports Loss of 40 Cents a Share, Wider Than Analysts' Estimates
-- JoAnne Norton
-- 2010-06-25T12:01:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-25/kb-home-reports-loss-of-40-cents-a-share-exceeding-analysts-estimates.html

          
          
             KB Home, the Los Angeles-based
builder specializing in homes for first-time buyers, had a
second-quarter loss of 40 cents a share. Analysts surveyed by
Bloomberg had estimated a loss of 31 cents on average.  
          
          


  


        